title: Ketsuinu
synopsis: Ketsuinu is a dog with a butt-like face. The unidentified creature comes out of nowhere and quickly multiplies. In the end, the owners' faces turn into butts...
staff: [['Kasugamori, Haruki', ['Director', ' Screenplay']], ['Iida, Satoki', ['Sound Director']], ['Mita, Jun', ['Key Animation']], ['Suzuki, Atsushi', ['Planning']]]
